{"tid":1850681,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有發國難財既藥房","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T17:25:28.000Z","uid":9047,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1b60f6f1005fb924e0fa470b1ca5fda66f856d14","tid":1850681,"uid":9047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"係呢一個月，相信大家都將身邊既藥房睇得清清楚楚，雖然本身好多藥房狗都係靠呃人黎搵食，但係到而家成個香港有難既時候你地瘋狂地坐地起價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼見由6月開始係藥房買物資39蚊50個口罩，到而家230蚊賣7個都有見過，要你用炒價買滴露不特些，重要你夾貨買又見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就連二手口罩都出埋黎<br />\n<br />\n他朝有日，香港到贏既時候，必定要向你地清算！！！<br />\n我建議可以好似和你eat咁整個黑心藥房list出黎慢慢報仇，清算呢班垃圾屎！<br />\n<br />\n煩都提多句，大家千奇唔好過份存貨，真係有好多人開始見底，如果有能力要同 真。香港人互相幫助！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重未買到口罩既手足頂住，一定要身體健康</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7b2e5a7a50040ffafe835d94a4d076269269462","tid":1850681,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:13:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1b138ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" 